structure.unit: COUNTY ROAD ENGINEER AND MAINTENANCE OF PUBLIC ROADS

law.history: Repealed 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 173, sec. 11. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 4356L-1 to 436L-5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: County engineer in counties of 200,000 population.
